divs: Sighting DetailsA thin white object was seen hovering near Boca Raton. A starlike dull yellow object like a "shooting star" passed around the first object in and out, up, down, hovering,fading and brightening then underneath the thin object.It faded and brightened. The thin object was brighter on one side than the other as though a light was going back and forth on its right side. Mary Margaret Zimmer FL ASD, FI
